title: Data to be saved in iCloud

cells.data:
1. obstacleInfoList: obstacleInfo - struct with all spawned obstacles information
  2. score: Int - current score
  3. level: Int - current level
  4. topMost: CGFloat - position of highest obstacle
  5. waterLevel: CGFloat - current water level
  6. steamLevel: CGFloat - current steamLevel
  7. backgroundObstacleInfo - list of all spawned background objects
  8. inAppPurchase ?? - track status of inApp purchases
